headline: Johnson Controls’ (JCI) Valuation Surged Sharply in Q2
summary: Cullen Capital Management, LLC, operating under the name Schafer Cullen Capital Management, Inc. (SCCM), has released its “SCCM Enhanced Equity Income Fund” second-quarter investor letter.
